-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-05/citigroup-seeks-to-block-finra-arbitration-of-383-million-claim.html
Citigroup Inc. (C)  is seeking to block
Financial Industry Regulatory Authority arbitration of a $383
million claim by Saudi investors who say the bank ‘wiped out’
their family’s wealth.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Bob Van Voris in New York at 
